data.description: This won't last long! If you're searching for a well kept home, in a tranquil neighborhood and still convenient location, this is it! The feeling of home comes as soon as you walk in with lots of windows to appreciate the  beautiful views everywhere! Kitchen has small island and opens into living area with gas fireplace and has a  lovely oak mantle. The eating area has  patio doors to the yard perfect for entertaining! 3 nice size bedrooms upstairs with a bonus room perfect for office/nursery/craft etc. The basement has extra light from an oversized access window all ready to finish, a  radon mitigation system and a sump pump. The roof is 2 years new and has the nice architectural shingles.Hvac system has newer condenser, blower, and heater. Nice size 2 car garage with 2 remotes. Several beautiful flower beds unfortunately not seen again until Spring!
